refsect1.para:
This function tries to modify either the target graph specified in the patch via guo:target_graph
(hence, the non-NULL target_graph argument of the diff creator, DB.DBA.RDF_SUO_DIFF_TTL()
) or the graph specified by default_target_graph argument. The function returns zero in case of success, non-zero value otherwise. In addition, the function produces a result set that describes the process of matching blank node in the target graph to instructions in the patch.
